{
  "stem": "1917.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 358.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They usually, my parents always helped them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So he came to the farm to try to grow some wheat and food, because Romania after the war was-- had no food whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And so my aunt-- and I didn't know that they knew about.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "There were-- the Israel-- the Jewish [INAUDIBLE] with the Red Cross had a complete list of transports for people coming back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "So my aunt knew a week in advance that we were on that train coming back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And my cousin came to [NON-ENGLISH] to get us to put us on the train to go back home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Well, I was very excited we were going back home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I didn't know what I would find.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "It was probably one of the most disappointing moment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "During the time that I was in the camp, there was almost like a slogan that we would get to say every day-- someday soon we will be free, and we will go home.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And we know the airplanes were coming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "So we would be free.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "The picture of home that I had in my mind was my mother, my father, my two older sisters with the twins.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And that picture was never again going to be realized.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "The house was completely ransacked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "The weeds were tall.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "There were-- was one bed in one room that my cousin got from somewhere so he could sleep on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "The floors were dirty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And there were three crumbled pictures in one of the bedrooms that I picked up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And there was my mother's dog, Lilly, was still alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And I looked at him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And I said, gosh, I guess Jewish dogs are not taken to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I did not want to stay there very long.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
